Upload case:
1) Look for remote in CONFIGDIR if --remote present.
2) Look for remote in dirname(case_dir) (The study is inside a case)
Upload study:
1) Look for remote in CONFIGDIR if --remote present.
2) Look for remote in case_dir (The study is inside a case)
Download study:
1) Download everything stated in params.yaml if DOWNLOAD section provided
2) If the data is not available to download it will show errors
3) --force option can be added to force download what is available and ignore the rest
